data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This immaculate, single-story gem boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing a perfect blend of comfort and style. The interior is adorned with exquisite granite countertops throughout, adding a touch of elegance to every corner. Natural light streams in through charming window shutters, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The modern kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making cooking a breeze. With its great condition, this home promises low-maintenance living and plenty of space for all your needs. Don't miss the chance to call this stunning property your own! Act fast - it won't stay on the market for long!
